}
note right of GameModel
    These are the methods available to the Controller.
    At the end of each method,
    the Model will notify the Controller (subscribed as a listener)
    about the changes in the state.
    These methods validate the parameters and invoke the methods
    of the class Match, which contains the actual state of the match.
end note

