note left of PatternObjectiveCard::coordReqPattern{
The pattern required to get points
is expressed as an array of 3 Coordinate
objects, representing the coordinates
and colours of the cards required by the
pattern, which can be seen either as a
3x3 submatrix or a 4x2 submatrix.
The coordinates represent the positions
of the cards in the submatrix.
}



