note left of GameCard::flagObj{
array of 8 boolean flags initialized to false:
each flag can be set to true if this instance
of a GoldCard object is used to count a
pattern objective card
e.g. flagObj[4] is set to true is this instance
of a GoldCard is used to count pattern objective
number 4 in the deck.
}


